msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"ANTI_ANAEROBIC_GRID\"]/title"
msgstr "Aero-Intolerance Grid"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5444
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"ANTI_ANAEROBIC_GRID\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"If an Oxygen system is present, all enemy anaerobic crew boarding your ship "
"will take 4HP/s of damage with an extra 2HP/s for each bar of power in your "
"Oxygen system. Science mumbo-jumbo has never been so satisfying to use!"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5452
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"SALVAGE_ARRAY\"]/title"
msgstr "Salvage Array"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5453
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"SALVAGE_ARRAY\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This is a combined modular arm that is both repairing the hull and "
"collecting bits of extra scrap. Though rusty and old, you're pretty sure "
"this array will hold out for long enough. Repairs the hull and increases "
"scrap rewards by 30%, taking 10% for repairs if necessary."

